        As a special bonus for waiting - if you sign up now as we work on perfecting the latest and greatest in <em>Chef</em> service we invite you to come <span style="font-weight: bold;">join us for a month FREE!</span> And you may never have to pay for the Chef service at all because it is easy to get it FREE FOREVER - Sign up now to learn how!
      </p>
      <p>
