      </p>
      <a href="https://new.ebtchef.com/public/signup?c=survey&e=<%=@user.email%>&h=<%=Promo.gen_hash('survey', @user.email)%>"><img src="http://new.ebtchef.com/images/emails/surveydeal/sign_up_now.png" alt="sign up NOW to learn how!" style="border: 0px;" /></a>
